# Frontend conventions

- Prefer functional components + hooks.
- Keep route components thin; move business logic to `src/features/` and backend logic to Convex.
- Avoid `any`; prefer `unknown` + narrowing.
- Use accessible, semantic HTML. Every form control needs a label.

